{"tid":2403517,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港府冒險引入 拒等埋世衞","createTime":"2021-02-11T06:42:27.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-11T06:54:15.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"bcd9dc08857c4401a44ca121a8f77c83027b0719","tid":2403517,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T06:42:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210211/DUABNQWYXRFYBMGK4JDCGD6L2E/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210211%2FDUABNQWYXRFYBMGK4JDCGD6L2E%2F&d=i0%2FHWd2N8RLCa1A1b4xPLA3x%2FUg%2Bgbtl8eFt0uNm3qw%3D&h=c3e2f110\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210211%2FDUABNQWYXRFYBMGK4JDCGD6L2E%2F&h=e91f002e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210211/DUABNQWYXRFYBMGK4JDCGD6L2E/</a><br />\n<br />\n港府冒險引入 拒等埋世衞<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/VxAHPuEX4IDEdwxHtjxhIuFHNbE=/1000x563/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/AANOMPC66FBCFGBLFJ3JY3AETI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FVxAHPuEX4IDEdwxHtjxhIuFHNbE%3D%2F1000x563%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FAANOMPC66FBCFGBLFJ3JY3AETI.jpg&h=f5efafe6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■科興疫苗最快3月抵港。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】網媒「香港01」報道，世衞預料本月底可收到科興提供更多資料，意味世衞最早下月才可審批科興疫苗，若香港兩周後批准科興疫苗在港緊急使用，將走在世衞之前。疫苗顧問專家委員會召集人劉澤星辯稱，世衞亦以相同方式審批疫苗，巴西、印尼、土耳其和智利亦已批准使用，委員會完全科學地研究數據，毋須等待世衞審批後才跟進。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：堂食、處所鬆綁 顧客須用安心出行或留資料  初七硬上碼 違者停業判監<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n無用於孕婦小孩等細節<br />\n<br />\n政府及委員會調低審批門檻，日後疫苗一旦出現嚴重事故，委員會會否負責？劉澤星說，委員均用「自己嘅心」和科學去評核數據，相信做法是正當，「將來會否錯，冇人知道，（委員會）會做咗個決定，個責任我哋一定要負啦」。資料顯示，劉澤星是全國政協副主席董建華與梁振英牽頭成立的「香港再出發大聯盟」的共同發起人之一，亦為粵港澳大灣區衞生與健康合作大會專家顧問，他曾拍片呼籲公眾參加普及社區檢測計劃。<br />\n<br />\n醫學會會長蔡堅估計，現時約。。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"f886760a8f04829f737578fdacefc4c953678c07","tid":2403517,"uid":387466,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T06:54:15.000Z","msg":"個責任我哋一定要負啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}